{"tid":1334963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[數據撚入] 關於反送中從五月到現在的一些統計 (多圖)","createTime":"2019-07-20T10:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:02:21.000Z","uid":282836,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e913ccd82b1a6fccafd414ef360929ba8011171","tid":1334963,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"數據由2019年1月1日至2019年7月19日<br />\n<br />\n紅色點或柱代表重要日期： 69, 612, 616, 71, 77, 714<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3On1bQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3On1bQ.png&h=d35e5060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖1a 每日總會員數 (1月至7月) , 橙線係增加率</span></div><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTbEiYw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTbEiYw.png&h=2433da5b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖1a 每日總會員數 (5月至7月)</span></div><br />\n從6月9日開始, 會員增加率以另一速度上升<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b933cfcdeb61e88eab09b76a8e8feeea8788172a","tid":1334963,"uid":282836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"<ins>第二part：連登仔團結指數</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔團結度(士氣%) = 正帖% - 負帖%, 得出下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/beFRbpJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbeFRbpJ.png&h=342c2147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖5a 連登團結指數 (1月至7月)</span></div> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPeiARp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPeiARp.png&h=1c466771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖5b 連登團結指數 (5月至7月)</span></div> <br />\n* 粗藍線=7天平均線<br />\n從5a圖1月至5月 團結指數